<h2 id="who-its-for">👥 Who Is Zen Planner For?</h2>

**Ideal fit:**
- Single-location CrossFit boxes, martial arts academies, and yoga studios
- Boutique fitness chains with 2-8 locations seeking standardized billing
- Operators prioritizing billing reliability over advanced marketing automation
- Gyms with 100-500 active members wanting predictable software costs
- Facilities needing workout programming and tracking alongside management tools

**Not ideal for:**
- Large gym chains (15+ locations) requiring enterprise reporting and analytics
- Operators heavily reliant on sophisticated marketing automation
- Facilities needing extensive third-party integrations
- 24-hour access gyms requiring robust access control integration
- Budget-constrained startups under 50 members (cost per member is high at small scale)

