<h2 id="alternatives">🔄 How Zen Planner Compares</h2>

Against **Mindbody**, Zen Planner offers simpler pricing and a more focused feature set. Mindbody provides broader marketplace exposure but costs more and includes features many gym operators never use. For pure-play fitness facilities, Zen Planner's specialization often proves more practical.

Against **Wodify**, the comparison is closer. Wodify has stronger CrossFit-specific features and a more modern interface, but Zen Planner's billing reliability edges ahead in our testing. Wodify's pricing runs slightly higher at comparable member counts.

Against **PushPress**, the newer competitor offers a more modern interface and competitive pricing, but lacks Zen Planner's track record and some depth in workout tracking. PushPress suits operators prioritizing interface polish over feature maturity.

For operators evaluating multiple platforms, our [membership management platform comparison](/reviews/membership-management-platforms-2026) provides side-by-side analysis of these options.

